{"tid":376928,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國龐大船隊非法捕魚損生態　加拉巴哥斯群島居民　連日上街抗議","createTime":"2017-08-27T10:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T11:50:05.000Z","uid":53379,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90e0d8f0da30a97abe3a86727b0e39cdbf751f21","tid":376928,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國龐大船隊非法捕魚損生態　加拉巴哥斯群島居民　連日上街抗議</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Galapagos-protest_Pbiuh_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FGalapagos-protest_Pbiuh_1200x0.png&h=ea99970b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國RFI報道，中國的龐大船隊在加拉巴哥斯群島（Gal&aacute;pagos Islands）海域非法濫捕珍貴海洋魚類激怒該島的居民。當地人從周三（8月23日）開始舉行3天的「哀悼」活動，同時上街遊行，抗議中國漁船破壞這個「人類遺產」海域的生態環境。該島因達爾文當年在此獲得「物種起源」的靈感而著稱於世。<br />\n<br />\n法新社8月26日報道說，厄瓜多爾的加拉巴哥斯群島（科隆群島）的居民三天來連續上街遊行，抗議中國龐大船隊的非法捕撈活動。周五，在抗議人群中，22歲少女Silvia Zabala向法新社表示：我們「守喪」三天，舉行示威活動，抗議非法捕魚。<br />\n<br />\n中國一艘名為「福遠魚冷999」（音譯）的漁船，因在加拉巴哥斯群島海域非法捕撈，8月13日被厄瓜多爾當局扣下。該國執法人員在船上發現包括「垂頭鯊魚」等瀕危物種在內的300噸魚類。20名中國船員已被拘押。他們被控非法捕撈，破壞生態環境，面臨1-3年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n法新社說，過去三年，曾有17艘掛厄瓜多爾旗的漁船因同樣原因被扣押。但非法捕撈規模最大的，是中國福遠魚冷999。除了這艘船身98米的漁船，還有300餘艘屬於該漁船公司的漁船在附近公海捕撈。<br />\n<br />\n加拉巴哥斯群島位於東太平洋，島上近乎「活化石」的動物和植物在全世界獨一無二。達爾文1835年9月到訪這個群島時，獲得了「進化論」的靈感，並在20後發表《物種起源》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%BE%90%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%B9%E9%9A%8A%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E6%90%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%A5%E6%96%AF%E7%BE%A4%E5%B3%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25BE%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%2590%258D%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2585%258B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2593%25A5%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&d=%2FMd9pphgY26K6J%2BQVtP%2F6gEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=2a313c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25BE%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%25B9%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%2590%258D%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2585%258B-%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%2593%25A5%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&h=75b83d9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%BE%90%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%B9%E9%9A%8A%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E6%90%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B-%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%89%E5%B7%B4%E5%93%A5%E6%96%AF%E7%BE%A4%E5%B3%B6%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"6af3d6dc1a6ddcec03ac1605823c96efceddf3e3","tid":376928,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"未富先驕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030eb7068111eefa11067c091de5fb02b19e8897","tid":376928,"uid":41695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"支那世界毒瘤 真係名不虛傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2754aa30ad6efb631a7a4230a1fbe1aad4a3a184","tid":376928,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"應該拉去打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddbb7674e144467d9edba0286fa8b1e05575b5a","tid":376928,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re